<h1 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.2;">Job posted successfully ✨</h1>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Hi <%= @company_name %>,</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Your job <strong style="color: #FE6711;">"<%= @job.title %>"</strong> has been posted and is now visible to technicians.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">View it in your dashboard to manage applications and messages.</p>

<%= render partial: 'user_mailer/cta_button', locals: { text: 'View in Dashboard', url: frontend_url('/dashboard') } %>
